name: Manulife Smart Defensive Equity ETF
longDescription: Manulife Smart Defensive Equity ETF seeks to achieve long-term capital appreciation. In order to achieve its investment objectives, Manulife Smart Defensive Equity ETF invests primarily in Canadian securities with a focus on securities with lower sensitivity to market changes. The Manager employs a proprietary defensive screen to select securities that are less market sensitive and optimizes Manulife Smart Defensive Equity ETF by allocating proportionally more assets to securities that have higher potential risk-adjusted returns.
